{
  "page": "Truth (book)",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><i><b>Truth</b></i> was written by <a href=\"/index.php/Maester\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Maester\">Maester</a> <a href=\"/index.php/Anson\" title=\"Anson\">Anson</a>. According to this work, the belief that <a href=\"/index.php/Dragons\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Dragons\">dragons</a> could change sex at need is erroneous, rooted in a misunderstanding of the metaphor that <a href=\"/index.php/Septon\" title=\"Septon\">Septon</a> <a href=\"/index.php/Barth\" title=\"Barth\">Barth</a> used when discussing higher mysteries.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_the_north:_winterfell.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf_the_north:_winterfell.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Truth_(book)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiaf_the_north:_winterfell.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_the_north:_winterfell.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>, The North: Winterfell.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403104733\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.017 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.037 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 101/1000000\nPreprocessor generated nod